data.description: Discover tranquility in this renovated 3-bed, 2-bath golf course home, boasting views of the 3rd Tee box. Newly painted interior and professionally painted exterior complement the new flooring, creating a stylish and inviting atmosphere. Updated bathrooms add modern convenience, while the parklike setting offers a serene escape. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a dog run, large side area for a shed or small trailer, and a fenced garden area. With its prime location and breathtaking views, this home is a must-see for golf enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Schedule your showing today!
